In Case of "Optimizing Web Performance"
 "simply run website "
  
  Open Chrome DevTools (Right-click > Inspect or Ctrl+Shift+I).

Go to the Lighthouse tab.

Run audits on both the unoptimized and optimized versions of the site.

Compare the scores for Performance, Accessibility, Best Practices, and SEO.

Key Changes
Images:

Converted large images to WebP format and added loading="lazy".

JavaScript:

Deferred the loading of JavaScript to prevent blocking the rendering of the page.

CSS:

Used minified CSS to reduce file size.
Accessibility:


Added for attributes to labels for better accessibility.

